profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

We specialize in designing homes, drafting the necessary construction drawings and then filing for the required building permits. 
This includes designing for new buildings, removal of a load-bearing wall, renovations, additions, garages, deck, basement conversions into suites and single-family home conversions into legal duplexes. 
We also provide client support and representation where a minor variance is required by the Committee of Adjustment. 
Do you have an upcoming construction project on your mind? 
Contact us today and we can offer you some helpful tips for getting started.

We are one of the most affordable places, which gives us the opportunity to provide you with an unbeatable quote keeping in mind the quality will stay intact of what you'll get in your place or better and we strongly believe that good relationships can maintain a healthy business.

Fine Finishes Design Inc. is a premier design and decorating firm serving the Greater Toronto area since 1997. 

We have a well earned reputation for attention to detail and professionalism in residential and commercial design.  Fine Finishes Design Inc. works closely with their clients and places special emphasis on understanding their unique needs, tastes and budget.  
Andrea Colman, the Principal Designer and Creative Director of Fine Finishes Design Inc. oversees each project personally ensuring the highest quality service.

Andrea graduated with the highest honours in the CIDC Design Program and is considered to be one of the best designers in the greater Toronto area.

Andrea is one of the founding members of The Benjamin Moore Painting and Decorating Services in North America and has sat on the Advisory Council for Benjamin Mooreâ€™s Painting and Decorating Services Canada.

Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling cost control and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

"My Prestigious Home" is where you need to be...

MPH has been a leader in major renovations and custom home construction since 2007. From concept to completion, we take a clientâ€™s vision and make it a reality through a comprehensive process to ensure the finished product exceeds expectations. Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your project and better to say, your investment. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, MPH is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.

Our vast professional experience, skilled expertise and attention to details enable us to offer you innovative solutions, competitive pricing and the ability to meet milestones. We appreciate how much your project means to you. Thatâ€™s why we approach each project with professionalism, integrity and adaptability while maintaining open communication with you every step of the way.
We pride ourselves in Home additions, renovations, custom home building, commercial renovations, condominium renovations and design and build projects.

We understand custom homes and renovations are amongst the most important investment to people in their lifetime. So whether it be a new architecturally designed or inspired home, or a renovation and extension of your existing home, you can be guaranteed that MPH is most definitely the qualified team for your project.

We have had the opportunity to transform your dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. We have enjoyed being a part of homeownersâ€™ lives and strive to continue to provide our customers with the best technology on the market. We have completed literally hundreds of renovations since our inception. 

Please view our website at http://MyPrestigiousHome.com to view images of some of our projects.

Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.

Our projects range from building new custom homes, home additions and extensions, condominium renovations, architectural design and permit, structural engineering, commercial renovations, rear addition, second floor addition, basement underpinning, custom kitchen and bathrooms, residential renovations and finally we design and build everything. We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship.

With 2 year Warranty, we at MPH know how to design and build lasting results and lasting relationships with each of our highly respected clients.

Our focus is on Custom projects such as custom Kitchen renovations, Basement Finishing and underpinning, Bathroom Renovation and Bathroom Remodeling, Home Additions, Second Story Additions, Rear Additions, Home Extensions and Rear Extensions, commercial renovations, office renovation, architectural drawings, permit and etc. We work with some of the top architects, interior designers, engineers and sub-trades in Toronto. We are the all inclusive General Contractor who will take care of all your design and general contracting needs.

MPH is an innovative, full service design/build/construction firm based in Toronto, specializing in residential clients across the GTA. With decades of construction management experience on a wide variety of residential projects, we offer a strong design aesthetic, invaluable insight, vast resources and craftsman that exceed client expectations.

Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling, cost control, and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

There are many different reasons to work with us: to make room for a growing family, to improve layout or increase the resale value of your property! Our team of professionals offer customers design and build counselling along with skilled trades and top discounts, on top brands.

There is no substitute for experience. Join the list of satisfied clients! In the end the quality of your project depends on who you hire. When you hire us, you do so because of our companyâ€™s reputation, our track record with past clients and our commitment to new ones.

Contact us for a free "No Pressure" estimate and let us help you take the first step to completing your project. Advice is always free. Remember, we are talking about Professional Advice from Skilled Engineer.
Our areas of servings are in Toronto, Beaches, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Richmond hill, Markham, Foresthill, Royal York, Vaughan, Woodbridge, East York, West end, Central Toronto, North York, & Downtown Toronto.

profile:
Chi-Noodin Sustainable Renovations applies a holistic approach to renovations, offering design + build for homes with sustainability in mind.
Mission - A Sustainable Proposition
Jeff and his team will work with you to reduce the environmental impact of your project by applying the right design philosophy, materials, equipment and construction methods while enhancing your comfort levels and reducing your energy bills.
Description
Chi-Noodin stands for "Big Wind". It is Jeff's Anishnawbe spirit name, "Big Wind that brings change to the people" It is this name that has given him the inspiration to apply a holistic approach to renovations, offering design + build for homes with sustainability in mind.

The Brief
Any given project is about the people and their story. Jeff will sit and listen carefully to this story and develop a design brief prior to creating physical plans. This will ensure that the end result matches the owner's requirements.

The Team
The client is central to any project team. Jeff will liaise directly with you throughout your project. He will assemble a team of professionals to suit the needs of the project. He will coordinate all efforts and be your single point of contact from start to finish.

Services
Depending on your location Jeff can provide all professional services within his team or work with your preferred local realtor, architect, engineer and licensed trades people. As a LEED Accredited Professional, Jeff will ensure that your project meets and exceeds the current building standards.

Great Value
By offering both design and build services, Jeff will be there to monitor progress from day one until the project is handed over to you, the client. With his architectural background he understands the intricacies of the multitude of disciplines involved and with his hands on construction experience he knows what it takes to really get the job done well. Jeff will be able to quote your project accurately and guarantee an excellent end result.

A Sustainable Proposition
Jeff and his team will work with you to reduce the environmental impact of your project by applying the right design philosophy, materials, equipment and construction methods while enhancing your comfort levels and reducing your energy bills.
name: Chi Noodin Sustainable Renovations

Corell Homes is a Tarion-Registered Toronto Custom Home Builder. We believe that constructing a home should be a fun and memorable experience - not a stressful one! Our unique style of building involves constant communication with the home owner throughout the entire process. Further to this, we have learned that cost overages and time delays are the two of the most stressful things that home owners fear. That is why our Fixed-Price and 200-Day Guarantees have become so popular. Simply put, we will lock-in your cost of building, and guarantee your home to be built within 200 days!

If you are looking for a Tarion builder to construct a custom home in Toronto, visit our website and contact us today!

profile:
BROOKVIEW FINE DECKS 

BUILD YOUR DREAM DECK OR BRING YOUR OLD WEATHERED DECK BACK TO LIFE! 

With over 20 years of Custom Deck Building experience, we offer a free comprehensive deck assessment whether building from scratch or restoring your weather beaten deck. 

We supply new deck quotes with custom drawings and the ability to change dimensions when required. 

We also offer deck repair and refinishing for those of you that just want to bring your deck back to it's original finish. A complete pressure washing with an environmentally friendly cleaning agent is applied and all dirt, grime, stain and mildew is removed. A light sanding to prepare the wood to accept the stain follows. After that, you are free to pick the color of your choice. All of this can be done in approximately 2 - 4 days. We will work within your schedule. 

Need a fence, gazebo or pergola built or restored? We will accommodate. 

CALL NOW FOR A FREE ESTIMATE! 
Office: 647-922-1853 

We service Toronto, Scarborough, Brampton, Etobicoke, Oshawa, Whitby, Ajax, Pickering, Mississauga, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Thornhill, King City, Markham, Aurora and Newmarket. 

Office Hours: 
Monday: 7am - 9pm 
Tuesday: 7am - 9pm 
Wednesday: 7am - 9pm 
Thursday: 7am - 9pm 
Friday: 7am - 9pm 
Saturday: 9am - 5pm 
Sunday: 9am - 5pm 

Estimates within 1 hour outside our service area will be billed $50.

profile: Are you looking for a custom built home in the Greater Toronto area? A custom home is the perfect solution for people with discerning taste. You have specific needs in mind when choosing a home that fits your lifestyle. Unlike sub division houses which are all basically cookie-cutter buildings inside and out, a custom home is built to your specifications. You, the home owner, have control over the layout, lot size, and amenities included in your new home. Our company was created because our existing customers were searching for their dream homes in neighborhoods they loved, but often couldnâ€™t find the home that matched. Our real estate knowledge of the best neighborhoods, combined with our building experience gives you the best of both worlds. When you work with us youâ€™ll find the neighborhood you love first and the home we build will suit your lifestyle. Best of all, it comes at a price that makes us incredibly competitive in the custom home field. We are committed to building the home you want at a price that is comparable to a sub division house. You get the home youâ€™ve always wanted without paying extra for being unique. We treat our customers with extreme care and consideration. After all, this is your dream home and it should reflect your personality while affording the comfort and pride of ownership.

Custom Home Building

Our custom homes are unique in every sense and designed to the highest standards. Whether your style is contemporary, modern or traditional we would be delighted to assist in creating your dream home.  Our experienced team transforms the design into reality, with great care and accuracy. We create designs that we know will be timeless and of the utmost quality. At Emberstone Homes we believe we excel in the distinctiveness of every detail, handcrafted in every single working step.  The natural character of wood, the skill of fine craftsmen, the exquisite look of the finish; thats how a one-of-a-kind home is created. â€‹

Construction  Management

Work one on one with us through the entire building process for a stress-free experience.

â€‹

Land Acquisition

profile:
Digital Design, Millwork & Fabrication
We help take your projects all the way from ideation to realization.
Whether you are a designer, a contractor, a person with an idea or a person with a space that needs a fit-out, millwork or piece of furniture, we will work with you every step of the way. 

We have two 5' x 10' (1524mm x 3048mm) 3 axis CNC router machines with a 10" Z-axis capability and more than seven years of experience offering CNC cutting services across Toronto, Canada and the United States. In this time we have realized numerous projects that were initially considered only possible with a 5 axis machine in sizes far beyond our machining area by various means we have become experienced with.

We offer high quality CNC cutting services, design, documentation, project management, interior design and millwork packages, prototyping, jigs and templating, assembly, finishing and installation. We are a turnkey solution.

profile:
Frontier Renovations & Design has been in business for 15(+) yrs and has been serving the GTA with quality renovations surpassing the average industry expectations. Our 25(+) yrs of experience offers our clients exceptional installation methods geared toward the diverse needs that are typical in the renovations industry. We have worked primarily on homes 60 years or older giving us the experience that is needed to successfully complete projects. We offer complete design/ build services for our clients.
 
Frontier Renovations & Design has had the great honor and privilege to employ our services on three hit TV shows for HGTV.
"INCOME PROPERTY" Seasons 4, 5 & 6- a show which offers homeowners the opportunity to have qualified Building Renovators to turn their single family dwelling into legal dual dwellings for the purpose of creating a passive income from their property, for 2-1/2 wonderfully successful seasons. 
New Projects
"Home to Win"- twenty two top HGTV designers and contractors design and renovate a dream home to be won by one of three lucky challengers in a battle royale: testing the creative and building practices of each team.
"$ave My Reno" Seasons 2, 3, & 4- homeowners reach out to Sebastian Clovis and Sabrina Smelko to help them with their home renovation that is on a strict budget. The homeowners invest sweat equity through assisting Sebastian and Sabrina with design, construction and Special Projects and custom builds.
